{
  "//": [
    "Hand-authored video records the title parser can't handle (tournament VODs etc.).",
    "scripts/parse.ts validates these and merges them into data/videos.json with",
    "parseConfidence 'manual' — they are authoritative, never parsed, never a parse failure.",
    "",
    "CONVENTION — tournament entries are SET-level: one record covers the whole set.",
    "teams[].characters is the UNION of champions that side fielded across the set",
    "(watch the VS screens), not a single game's duo. Pairing/matchup stats only count",
    "a side when its union is exactly 2 champions; usage stats always count everything.",
    "",
    "Fields per entry (see ManualVideoEntry in types/index.ts):",
    "  id            YouTube video id — required, must not collide with a parsed video",
    "  title         real video title — required",
    "  publishedAt   ISO timestamp — required (drives season fallback + date sort)",
    "  tournament    event name, e.g. 'Evo 2026' — required",
    "  round         bracket round label, e.g. 'Grand Final' — optional",
    "  channelName   hosting YouTube channel — optional, defaults to the tournament name",
    "  thumbnail     optional, defaults to https://i.ytimg.com/vi/<id>/hqdefault.jpg",
    "  durationSec   optional, default 0    viewCount  optional, default 0",
    "  matchType     optional, default 'tournament'",
    "  season        optional, defaults from publishedAt via seasonBoundaries.json",
    "  patch         optional, default null    tags  optional extra tags",
    "  todo          optional free-text marker — parse warns but proceeds; remove when done",
    "  teams         exactly 2, in title order (left, right):",
    "    players     display names — resolved against players.json aliases;",
    "                unknown names are registered as new verified players",
    "    characters  champion ids or aliases — validated, unknown ids are a hard error;",
    "                use [] while unknown (pair with a todo)",
    "    fuse        optional fuse id, default null",
    "",
    "TEMPLATE — copy, fill, drop the todo when characters are in:",
    "  { \"id\": \"XXXXXXXXXXX\", \"title\": \"…\", \"publishedAt\": \"2026-01-01T00:00:00Z\",",
    "    \"tournament\": \"…\", \"round\": \"…\", \"channelName\": \"…\",",
    "    \"durationSec\": 0, \"viewCount\": 0,",
    "    \"todo\": \"fill teams[].characters from the VS screens\",",
    "    \"teams\": [ { \"players\": [\"…\"], \"characters\": [] },",
    "               { \"players\": [\"…\"], \"characters\": [] } ] }"
  ],
